        "## Least squares and QR\n",
        "\n",
        "### Theorem 10.14: Least squares by projection\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-important}\n",
        "For an overdetermined system\n",
        "$$\n",
        "Ax\\approx b,\n",
        "$$\n",
