        "<summary>Proof</summary>\n",
        "\n",
        "The vector $A\\widehat x$ is the projection of $b$ onto $\\operatorname{Col}(A)$. Therefore the residual\n",
        "$$\n",
        "r=b-A\\widehat x\n",
        "$$\n",
        "is orthogonal to every column of $A$. This is exactly\n",
        "$$\n",
        "A^Tr=0.\n",
        "$$\n",
        "Substituting $r=b-A\\widehat x$ gives the normal equations.\n",
        "\n",
